name: Free black futon couch (Round Rock - Cat Hollow)
description:
Black futon couch. Mechanically and structurally okay. Pretend-leather upholstery is flaking off -- mostly on the seat section. Back lays flat to make a bed. It's about 5 1/2 feet wide and all one piece.

It's on the curb at 6068 Almelo Dr in Round Rock. Free to the first person to come get it.
